title: 266 - Cloud 9 Joggers
description:
MATERIAL: 80% Fleece Cotton, 20% Polyester. Do Not Tumble Dry. HANG DRY ONLY.

FIT: Loose.

DESIGN: Cloud 9 joggers are the perfect companion for the fall season, offering unparalleled softness and comfort. These joggers are designed to provide a cozy feel, making them perfect for lounging at home or a casual outing. Available in earthy colors, the Cloud 9 joggers feature a loose-fitting design for flexibility and freedom of movement. Experience the ultimate in comfort and style all season long.

MODEL: The model in the first photo is wearing a size Medium. Weight: 175lb Height: 5'9.
